snippet.textDisplay:
The trampoline was designed by Mark Rober and the plans were sent to Perth, to guys who live near the tower. How Ridiculous also teamed up with Springfree Trampoline in the past.


The Tweet was sent out to Mark Rober on Sep. 6, 2019.


The trampoline's springs collectively can handle about 68,400LBS or a little under 30,000KG


They used 144 garage door springs


I will say it costs about $4,932.45
